name: SOCIAL EMPOWERMENT OF YOUTH WOMEN AND CHILDREN
briefDescription: SEYWAC undetakes transformational programs that empower our children, youth and women. SEYWAC helps many under privileged students who go to government schools by donating books, a pair of cloths, or paying tuition fee for poor and providing special educational camps during exams. SEYWAC also involved in e-governance projects, taking Information Technology to villages and farmers.
